@node Intro, Installation, Top, Top
@chapter About BDSIM

BDSIM is a particle tracking code designed for accurate simulation of particle
transport in high energy accelerator beam lines. It combines fast tracking 
techniques in conventional electromagnetic fields with Monte-Carlo simulations of various 
particle interactions. It is intended to use in such problems as collimation
design, background studies, laser beam diagnostics etc. 
 

