@node Cards,,,
@section Input Cards


The execution of @code{BDSIM} is controlled by parameters specified in the
input cards file. It has the following format


@var{card-name} @var{card-value}

Possible card names are 

@table @samp

@item ACCELERATOR

Accelerator name

@item BUNCH_TYPE

@item USE_JOB

@item TUNNEL_RADIUS

@item BEAMPIPE_RADIUS

@item TURN_ON_SYNCHROTRON

@end table


